Package org.conical.common.bbl.enums.ifc

Interface Coded

All Known Implementing Classes:
Ethnicity, Handedness, Race, Sex
public interface Coded
This interface helps ensure that enum values that have integer equivalents (usually stored in database tables) are easily distinguishable from those that aren't. The return value for the lone method should be the int value stored when this enum value is chosen.
Author:
rdoherty
